96d5f7c6e7a8f20f228facdb","tid":28894,"uid":35653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:41:28.000Z","msg":"中華牌鉛筆一支"},{"pid":"070af243d1377de4bb0486b05448b1a4b57d6026","tid":28894,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"小學受過某銀行贈品縮骨遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為嗰日落雨，我攞嗰時仲係濕嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfa1eb9e46b5fef991ea0ece5c4a98bb3ab1ed2","tid":28894,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:58:06.000Z","msg":"都係小學嘅事：<br />\n某條八婆攞咗垃圾賀卡出嚟抽奬，俾我朋友抽中左<br />\n下年我朋友拎返張卡出嚟抽奬，點知條八婆抽中返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個八婆竟然即刻舉手話收到垃圾叫班主任評理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果老師要我朋友將佢抽到份新的禮物同候八婆換返張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話係懲罰佢小氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有不滿就應該上年就講出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40659dbda1c607399dbba74297d45e8f11197012","tid":28894,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"中學就冇得玩交換禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係每人交多十蚊班會費，連埋老師貼錢俾班會啲人出去買，有幾份係貴野/大公仔，其他係嗰啲十蚊舖貨色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以都冇咩伏野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n抽到嘅都係筷子 扇嗰啲普通野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有年係兔公仔，仲放咗喺床頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cc93ca4754eedd043252be5a95a83febec5aa8","tid":28894,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:10:30.000Z","msg":"小學雞送過文具套裝<br />\n筆呀記事簿一堆樣樣有啲，有啲我都唔捨得用，嗰陣仲搵埋花紙包住，心唸都算得體掛，真心膠咁覺得都算唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知見到收到個人屌晒鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻繼續食嘢扮唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾唸唸下，呢啲雜嘜牌文具我就覺得靚姐，人哋有錢女鬼稀罕呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋又花紙包到實一實，咁人哋落差大嬲都正常嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋個年我都係收返一本筆記簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a62b9c1b12eda675979f778ac0f56ebb1ceb01","tid":28894,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:13:22.000Z","msg":"中學個陣試過專登買個ps3吉盒返黎<br />\n入面再裝本字典<br />\n<br />\n抽中個位同學足足屌左我一年老母"},{"pid":"535c650961d9d14fcdd537233036d8c58f8b2bf5","tid":28894,"uid":31911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>8KG金象米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上年正正買左呢樣做禮物抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7f0ec387d2f0fb3156af27da9709a3aca96f95","tid":28894,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"KY"},{"pid":"e0dd220b471d2486558616839304f38dd4b69a59","tid":28894,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquo